  "texts": [
    "All linear mixed-effects models were conducted using the \"lme4\" package of R software version 3.3.1.",
    "In different group analyses, the difference in the lung function parameters and 95% CIs between the two groups were presented.",
    "A total of 60 participants were screened, and 47 were enrolled and underwent randomization (24 were assigned to the Qiju group and 23 were assigned to the placebo group).",
    "Among those, 40 participants completed the scheduled follow-ups; of which 20 were in the Qiju group and 20 were in the control group",
    "Characteristics of the participants at baseline."
  ],
